headline: Old Dominion Freight Line, Inc. Announces General Rate Increase
summary: THOMASVILLE, N.C., November 18, 2024--Old Dominion Freight Line, Inc. (Nasdaq: ODFL) today announced a general rate increase (GRI) of 4.9 percent applicable to rates established under the existing ODFL 559, 670, and 550 tariffs, effective December 2, 2024.
